wift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/coordinate":{"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/coordinate","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/coordinate","title":"coordinate","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"coordinate","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The center point (specified as a map coordinate) of the annotation. (required)","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"(read-only)","type":"text"}]}}}